{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding the learning model, different configurations of SVM (BoW with non-linear kernel, word2vec with linear kernel, and word2vec with non-linear kernel) were explored.",
    "This study is the first to report the Matthews Correlation Coefficient (MCC) metric.",
    "Experimental results depicted that adding reference data has potential in the automation of citation screening.",
    "More recently, text classification for abstract screening has shifted towards the use of RNNs and LLMs.",
    "Hasny et al. (2023), is one of the newer papers to investigate the use of BERT and its biomedical variants for title and abstract screening for complex SR datasets."
  ]
}